@AbapCatalog.viewEnhancementCategory: [#NONE]
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Lojistik Raporu SAS Listesi Detay'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
@ObjectModel.usageType:{
    serviceQuality: #X,
    sizeCategory: #S,
    dataClass: #MIXED
}
define view entity YI_NFT_DDL_IMP_LOGIS_PO_DETAIL
  as select from    ynft_t_dlvit_cus         as dlvit
    inner join      ynft_t_dlv_cus           as dlv      on dlv.deliverydocument = dlvit.deliverydocument
    inner join      I_PurchaseOrderItemAPI01 as ekpo     on  ekpo.PurchaseOrder     = dlvit.purchaseorder
                                                         and ekpo.PurchaseOrderItem = dlvit.purchaseorderitem
    left outer join YI_NFT_DDL_IMP_COST_DATA as costdata on  costdata.DeliveryDocument     = dlvit.deliverydocument
                                                         and costdata.DeliveryDocumentItem = dlvit.deliverydocumentitem
{
  key dlvit.deliverydocument,
  key dlvit.deliverydocumentitem,
      dlvit.purchaseorder,
      dlvit.purchaseorderitem,
      @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure: 'PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit'
      costdata.deliveryquantity,
      ekpo.PurchaseOrderQuantityUnit,
      dlvit.incentivedocument,
      dlvit.incentivedocumentitem,
      dlvit.controldocument,
      dlvit.invoicedocument,
      dlvit.invoicedate,
      dlvit.gtipno,
      dlvit.origin,
      dlv.deliverydate,
      dlv.loadingdate,
      dlv.billoflading,
      dlv.documenttype,
      dlv.customsgate,
      dlv.customsreceivedate,
      dlv.invoiceno,
      dlv.fictitiousdeclerationdate,
      dlv.fictitiousdeclerationno,
      dlv.customsdeclerationdate,
      dlv.customsdeclerationno,
      dlv.importdate
}
